#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:1
msgid "Creating a new project"
msgstr "建立一個新專案"

#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:3
msgid ""
"When you create a new project with Cargo, it will automatically add "
"configuration for the latest edition:"
msgstr ""

#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:6
msgid ""
"```console\n"
"> cargo +nightly new foo\n"
"     Created binary (application) `foo` project\n"
"> cat foo/Cargo.toml\n"
"[package]\n"
"name = \"foo\"\n"
"version = \"0.1.0\"\n"
"edition = \"2021\"\n"
"\n"
"[dependencies]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:18
msgid ""
"That `edition = \"2021\"` setting will configure your package to use Rust "
"2021. No more configuration needed!"
msgstr ""

#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:21
msgid ""
"If you'd prefer to use an older edition, you can change the value in that "
"key, for example:"
msgstr ""

#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:24
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[package]\n"
"name = \"foo\"\n"
"version = \"0.1.0\"\n"
"edition = \"2015\"\n"
"\n"
"[dependencies]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[package]\n"
"name = \"foo\"\n"
"version = \"0.1.0\"\n"
"edition = \"2015\"\n"
"\n"
"[dependencies]\n"
"```"

#: src/editions/creating-a-new-project.md:33
msgid "This will build your package in Rust 2015."
msgstr ""
